    All Classes and Interfaces

    Classes
    Class
    Description
    Main
    Main class that solves the Student Project Allocation Problem with a greedy algorithm
    Person
    Represents a person with their name and date of birth.
    Problem
    Represents a problem with a name, a solution, a list of students that are solving this problem, a list of teachers that assigned this problem and a list of projects in which this problem is present.
    Project
    Represents a project with a name, a set of problems, a student which is assigned this project and a teacher that assigned that project.
    Solution
    Represents the solution to a problem with a name.
    Student
    Represents a student with a registration number, a list of preferred projects and a project he is assigned to.
    Teacher
    Represents a teacher with a list of proposed projects.
